<section id="To_set_the_location_of_the_Log_Depot" remap="TID_15037">
	<title>Setting the Location of the Log Depot</title>
	<procedure>
		<title>To Set the Location of the Log Depot</title>
		<step>
			<para>
				Navigate to <menuchoice><guimenu>Configure</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configuration</guisubmenu></menuchoice>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click the <guilabel>Diagnostics</guilabel> accordion, then click the <guilabel>Zone</guilabel> that you want to view.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click <guibutton>Collect Logs</guibutton>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/1851.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> (<guilabel>Edit the Log Depot Settings for the selected Zone</guilabel>).
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Select the <guilabel>Type</guilabel> of share.
			</para>
			<mediaobject>
				<imageobject>
					<imagedata align="center" fileref="images/6254.png" />
				</imageobject>
			</mediaobject>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Using the fully qualified domain name (FQDN) of the depot server, type in the appropriate settings for the <guilabel>URI</guilabel>.
			</para>
			<mediaobject>
				<imageobject>
					<imagedata align="center" fileref="images/6259.png" />
				</imageobject>
			</mediaobject>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				If required, enter your user ID and password then click <guibutton>Validate</guibutton> to confirm the settings.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click <guibutton>Save</guibutton>.
			</para>
		</step>
	</procedure>
</section>